<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer16623453920052343201">Marja Verschoor-Meijers was born and raised in the Netherlands. She is a freelance writer, speaker, and award winning author of several books on Christian living. Her books have been translated in Dutch, German, Farsi, Italian, Polish, Russian, Slovak, and Spanish. She writes weekly on her weblog ‘Fresh Insights on Ancient Truths’.<br/><br/>Together with her husband Jan she is the co-founder of the non-prof</span>
  <span id="freeText16623453920052343201" style="display:none">Marja Verschoor-Meijers was born and raised in the Netherlands. She is a freelance writer, speaker, and award winning author of several books on Christian living. Her books have been translated in Dutch, German, Farsi, Italian, Polish, Russian, Slovak, and Spanish. She writes weekly on her weblog ‘Fresh Insights on Ancient Truths’.<br /><br />Together with her husband Jan she is the co-founder of the non-profit organization Traveling Light. They offer practical help, financial support and spiritual encouragement to ministries all over Europe and the Middle East.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16623453920052343201" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
</div>

